&lt;p&gt;Commissioning &amp; Development Support Officer&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NHS County Durham CCG is pleased to invite applications for the role of Commissioning and Development Support. The post is being advertised as a 12-month secondment, or 12-month fixed term contract, to cover a vacancy within the team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for someone who enjoys working as part of a team and can demonstrate a commitment to delivering a high quality service; to improve outcomes for patients through effective project management and robust performance management of primary care services. You will need to be able to work under pressure, be responsive to fast moving deadlines and maintain constructive relationships with a broad range of stakeholders.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be part of the Primary Care Team which will support programmes of work and will have responsibility for delivering on a range of initiatives which forms part of the CCG’s work plan.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further information please contact Juliet Carling julietcarling@nhs.net 07920467422&lt;/p&gt;
